natural_language: The system will not install updates unless there is enough disk space and the update is available.
The application will not launch unless the operating system is updated and the user is logged in.
The feature will not be enabled unless the user is authenticated and the feature is available.
The service will not start automatically unless auto mode is selected and the service is configured.
The device will not enter sleep mode unless there have been 5 minutes of inactivity and the device is idle.
llm_output: DEVICE_IN_SLEEP_MODE IMPLIES (NOT DEVICE_ACTIVE FOR 300 SECONDS) AND NOT DEVICE_BUSY

natural_language: Notifications will not appear unless do not disturb mode is disabled and the phone is switched on.
The backup will not proceed unless the storage device is connected and backup is enabled.
The system will not reboot unless all critical processes have completed and a reboot is requested.
The settings will not be saved unless the form is validated and the user has confirmed.
The connection will not be established unless the network is available and a connection is requested.
